# FizzBuzz - a classic programming challenge
say "FizzBuzz from 1 to 30:"

set i to 1
repeat while i is at most 30:
    if i % 15 is 0:
        say "FizzBuzz"
    otherwise if i % 3 is 0:
        say "Fizz"
    otherwise if i % 5 is 0:
        say "Buzz"
    otherwise:
        say i
    set i to i + 1
